<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Organizer FAQ | Platform</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    .faq-container { max-width: 800px; margin: 4rem auto; padding: 2rem; }
    .faq-item { background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-radius: 12px; }
    .faq-question { font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.2rem; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .faq-answer { color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }
    .faq-highlight { color: var(--accent-gold); font-weight: 600; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <div class="faq-container">
    <h1 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: white;">Organizer FAQ</h1>
    <p style="text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      Empowering competition organizers with unparalleled digital reach and brand visibility.
    </p>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">Why should I upload my results here instead of just my website?</div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        When you upload your results to our platform, they are instantly, permanently linked to the <span class="faq-highlight">digital portfolios of thousands of dancers and studios</span>. Instead of a static PDF that gets lost over time, your awards become dynamic trophies that dancers share on social media, use for college recruiting, and embed on their studio websites—giving your organization massive, ongoing brand visibility.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">How does custom branding work?</div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        When you claim your Organizer profile, you can upload your official logo. Our system will automatically embed your custom logo onto the "Trophy Cards" displayed on dancer profiles, completely replacing the generic site logo. This turns every award won at your event into an enduring advertisement for your competition.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">What file formats are supported for upload?</div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        You can upload standard <span class="faq-highlight">.CSV</span> or <span class="faq-highlight">.XLSX (Excel)</span> files directly from your scoring system. Once uploaded, our AI will automatically parse the data, verify it, and seamlessly integrate it into the dancer and studio portfolios.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">How do the analytics help my organization?</div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        Your dashboard provides deep demographic insights that you can't get anywhere else. We track the lifetime performance of studios across the country. You can see how many unique studios attend your events, your year-over-year retention rate, and geographic heatmaps to help you decide where to expand your tour next season.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">Can I link my registration portal?</div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        Yes! On your verified historical results pages, we can embed a prominent "Register for Next Year" button. This captures dancers and studio owners right when they are checking their results and are most engaged with your brand.
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
